description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/ParaShare La Llorona & The Whispers of the Dead Edition

Dave & Tim get eerie on your asses with a new set of supernatural news from around the world! A ghost tries to call for help from beyond the grave to solve her murder, La Llorona is making a silent vigil and terrifying passersby, haunted castles, a strange house that compels people to jump from its roof AND your stories of real paranormal encounters PLUS a Brand New Theater of the Mind!

Check out the news here: www.darknessradio.com/news

Check out our shop here: www.darknessradio.com/store
